{"id":311625,"type":2,"name":"まんが ふるさと昔ばなし","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f4/29/311625_W437Q.jpg","summary":"『まんがふるさと昔話』（まんがふるさとむかしばなし）は、1976年8月6日から同年12月24日まで東京12チャンネル（現・テレビ東京）で放送されていたテレビアニメである。\r\n日本各地の昔話をテレビアニメ化した作品。1回につき2話を放送する方式であった。登場人物たちの声は主に松島トモ子と牟田悌三が当てていたが、別の人物が担当することもあった 。松島は、本作主題歌の歌唱担当者でもあった。\r\n本放送時には西武百貨店の単独提供番組で、「西武ファミリー劇場」をタイトルに冠していた。放送時間は毎週金曜 19:30 - 20:00 （日本標準時）。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>漫画故乡昔话</li><li><span>话数: </span>26</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1976-08-06</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>金</li><li><span>别名: </span>まんが ふるさと昔話</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Manga Furusato Mukashibanashi</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Animation of World Folklore</li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>東京12チャンネル（現 テレビ東京）</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1976-12-10</li><li><span>演出: </span>上野寿夫、福田元彦</li><li><span>脚本: </span>上野寿夫、福田元彦</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"eps":[{"id":968108,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968108","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968109,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968109","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968110,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968110","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968111,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968111","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968112,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968112","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968113,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968113","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":968114,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/968114","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status